DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN
       Erf(x) returns the error	function of x; where

       erf(x) =	2/sqrt(pi)*integral from 0 to x	of exp(-t*t) dt.

       Erfc(x) returns 1.0-erf(x).

       The  entry for erfc is provided because of the extreme loss of relative
       accuracy	if erf(x) is called for	large x	and the	result subtracted from
       1.  (e.g. for x = 10, 12	places are lost).

